title: Teenage boy dead after ute rolls over on rural property - Yahoo7
text:
Teenage boy dead after ute rolls over on rural property - Yahoo7 A 16-year-old boy has died when a ute rolled over in rural Victoria overnight. Close Teen killed riding back of ute UP NEXT VIDEO Teen killed riding back of ute. Source: 7 News Teen killed riding back of ute 
It is believed the boy was riding in the back of the ute when it rolled on a private property at Gladysdale about 7:30pm yesterday. A teen has died after a ute he was in rolls over. Photo: 7 News The driveway to the rural property where a ute rolled over killing a teenaged boy. 
Police arrested the alleged 20-year-old driver at the scene, but he's since been released. 
Two other passengers in the vehicle suffered minor injuries.
